titleStmt.title: Edward T. Newell notebook on coins at the British Museum, undated

note.p: Notebook containing handwritten notes on ancient Greek coins at the British Museum, London. The names C.W. Oman and James Leigh Strachan-Davidson, master of Balliol, appear in the first pages. Four loose sheets of rubbings are included.

monogr.title: Edward T. Newell notebook on coins at the British Museum, undated
monogr.extent: circa 200 pages ; 10 x 6 cm + 4 loose sheets.
